      <title>马来西亚大华银行资产在纳入印度债券基金之前推出印度债券基金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-05/malaysia-s-uob-asset-launches-india-bond-fund-before-inclusion</link>
